    "{\n",
    " \"cells\": [\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"# Meme Text Classifier\\n\",\"**NLP Project 72 of 100** — Classify meme captions by theme or sentiment.\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"import numpy as np, pandas as pd, matplotlib.pyplot as plt, seaborn as sns\\nfrom sklearn.feature_extraction.text import TfidfVectorizer\\nfrom sklearn.linear_model import LogisticRegression\\nfrom sklearn.metrics import accuracy_score, classification_report\\nfrom sklearn.model_selection import train_test_split\\nimport warnings; warnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\\nsns.set_style('whitegrid')\\n%matplotlib inline\\nSEED = 42; rng = np.random.default_rng(SEED)\\nprint('Loaded.')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"memes = {\\n    'Humor': ['When the code works on first try','Me pretending to understand the meeting','Nobody: My cat at 3am','POV: its Monday again'] * 20,\\n    'Motivation': ['You got this keep going','Believe in yourself today','Every expert was once a beginner','Hard work beats talent'] * 15,\\n    'Sarcasm': ['Oh great another meeting that could be an email','Sure let me just work overtime for free','Wow what a surprise the deadline moved again'] * 18,\\n    'Relatable': ['Me trying to adult','When you finally understand the assignment','My brain during an exam vs after','Sleep schedule what sleep schedule'] * 17,\\n}\\nrows = []\\nfor theme, texts in memes.items():\\n    for t in texts:\\n        rows.append({'text': t.lower(), 'theme': theme})\\ndf = pd.DataFrame(rows).sample(frac=1, random_state=SEED).reset_index(drop=True)\\nprint(f'Shape: {df.shape}'); print(df['theme'].value_counts())\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"X_train, X_test, y_train, y_test = train_test_split(df['text'], df['theme'], test_size=0.2, random_state=SEED)\\ntfidf = TfidfVectorizer(max_features=3000, ngram_range=(1,2))\\nX_tr = tfidf.fit_transform(X_train); X_te = tfidf.transform(X_test)\\nlr = LogisticRegression(max_iter=500, random_state=SEED)\\nlr.fit(X_tr, y_train)\\ny_pred = lr.predict(X_te)\\nprint(f'Accuracy: {accuracy_score(y_test, y_pred):.4f}')\\nprint(classification_report(y_test, y_pred))\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Summary\\n\",\"- **Meme text classification detects themes** like humor, sarcasm, and motivation.\\n\",\"- **Short, informal text is challenging** but TF-IDF captures key patterns.\\n\",\"- **For production, combine text + image features** for multimodal classification.\"]}\n",
    " ],\n",
